Gerard "Jerry" Host, president and 
chief executive officer of Trustmark National Bank, discusses 
his company's banking, lending operations and shareholder 
returns.  Host talked with Bloomberg's  Kathleen Hays  and Vonnie 
Quinn on "The Hays Advantage" on Bloomberg Radio on March 1, 
2012.   (Source: Bloomberg)  Running time 12:59
 